                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script" cert="medium">Nineteenth-century script.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red.</seg>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Divine names, chapter titles and numbers, some
                           incipits, some punctuation marks, some Ethiopic numerals as well as
                           occasionally the word <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡</foreign>.</seg>
                        <desc>Regular, neat, careful.</desc>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>


                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d1" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#1v"/>
                        <desc><persName ref="PRS9684Uriel"/> gives <persName ref="PRS3943Ezra"/> the
                           cup of wisdom. <q xml:lang="am">ቅዱስ፡ ዑራኤል፡ ለነቢዩ፡ ለእዝራ፡ ጽዋዓ፡ ልቡና፡ እንዳጠጣው።
                              እዝራ፡ ጽዋዓ፡ ልቡና፡ በዑራኤል፡ እጅ፡ እንዳጠጣ።</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d2" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#2r"/>
                        <desc>Two Ethiopian monks: <persName ref="PRS8711sehmas"/> and <persName
                              ref="PRS14471AkalaKrestos"/>. A serpent is swallowing the beard of
                              <persName ref="PRS14471AkalaKrestos"/>, while the holy monk is
                           absorbed in prayer. <q xml:lang="am">አባ፡ ጽሕማ። አቡነ፡ አካለ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘሀገረ፡ ነጋሳ፡
                              ከሚጸልዩበት፡ ዘንድ፡ አፋቸውን፡ እንጎራሳቸው፡</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d3" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#5v"/>
                        <desc>A miniature of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild"
                           /> and two <term key="angel">Angels</term>. <q xml:lang="am">ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡
                              ምስለ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወልዳ፡ እግዝእት፡ ማርያም፡ ቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d4" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#10v"/>
                        <desc>A miniature of St. <persName ref="PRS10581Zamika"/>. <q xml:lang="am"
                              >አቡነ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ዘደብረ፡ ዳሞ<supplied reason="omitted"
                        >።</supplied></q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d5" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#29v"/>
                        <desc>A miniature of St. <persName ref="PRS8491Samuel"/>. <q xml:lang="am"
                              >አቡነ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ዘሀገረ፡ ዋልድባ።</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d6" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#43r"/>
                        <desc>The miracle of St. <persName ref="PRS6006Kiros"/>. <q xml:lang="am"
                              >ክርስቶስም፡ ቃልኪዳን፡ እንደሰጣቸው፡ አቡነ፡ ኪሮስ፡ አርባ፡ ዓመት፡ ከመሬት፡ ውድቀው፡ እንደጸለዩና፡ ሰር፡
                              እንደበቀለባቸው፡</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d7" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#46v"/>
                        <desc>A miniature of <persName ref="PRS6751Mark"/></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d8" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#101r"/>
                        <desc>A miniature of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1012Equestrian"/>,
                              <persName ref="PRS4585Georgeo"/> slaying the dragon. <q xml:lang="am"
                              >ቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ድራጎንን፡ እንደገደለ፡ ቢራታዊትን፡ እንዳደነ፡</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d9" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#112r"/>
                        <desc>Two episodes of the martyrdom of <persName ref="PRS4585Georgeo"/>. <q
                              xml:lang="am">ቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስን፡ <sic>ከመለት፡</sic> ቤት፡ <choice>
                                 <sic>አገብተ፡</sic>
                                 <corr>አገቡት፡</corr>
                              </choice> እንዳሰሩት፡ የቤቱን፡ ምሰሶ፡ ዘተሰራበት፡ እንዳለመለመው። ቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስን፡ ሶስት፡ ልሳን፡
                              ብረት፡ አግለው፡ በመቀመጨውና፡ በጅ፡ በግሩ፡ እንደቸንከሩት፡</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d10" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#112v"/>
                        <desc>A miniature of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1030Trinity"/> with
                           the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1014Evangelists"/>. <q xml:lang="am"
                              >ገጸ፡ ስብእ፡ ገጸ፡ ንስር፡ ገጸ፡ አንበሳ፡ ገጸ፡ ላህም፡ ቅድስት፡ ሥላሴ፡ አብ፡ ወልድ፡ መንፈስ፡
                              ቅዱስ፡</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d11" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#113r"/>
                        <desc><persName ref="PRS7049Michael"/> and <persName ref="PRS4377Gabriel"/>.
                              <q xml:lang="am">ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤልና፡ ቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ከሥላሴ፡ ምሕረት፡
                                 <choice><sic>እንዱለመኑ፡</sic><corr>እንደለመኑ፡</corr></choice></q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d12" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#186v"/>
                        <desc><persName ref="PRS4306GabraMa"/> with <term key="animal">lions and
                              leopards</term>. <q xml:lang="am">አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘደብረ፡ ዝቋላ፡ ስሳ፡
                              እናብስት፡ ስሳ፡ አናምርት፡ እንደተከተሏቸው።</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d13" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#187r"/>
                        <desc><persName ref="PRS9162TaklaHa"/>. <q xml:lang="am">አቡነ፡ ተክለሐይማኖት፡
                              ዘደብረ፡ ሊባኖስ።</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d14" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#187v"/>
                        <desc>A miniature of the <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1065RoadtoCalvary"
                           />. <q xml:lang="am">ኵርአተ፡ ርእሱ፡ ለመድኃኔዓለም።</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d15" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#188r"/>
                        <desc><persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/> carrying the <term key="cross"/>. <q
                              xml:lang="am">ማርቆስ፡ ምዕራፍ፡ ፲፭ቁጥር፡ ፳፩።</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d16" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#188v"/>
                        <desc><q xml:lang="en">Woman, behold your son</q>. <q xml:lang="am">ሕያው፡
                              መድኃኔዓለም። እምቤታችን፡ እግረ፡ መስቀል፡ እንዳለቀሰች<supplied reason="lost"
                                 >።</supplied> ዮሐንስ፡ <choice>
                                 <sic>ፍቁራ</sic>
                                 <corr>ፍቁሩ</corr>
                              </choice>፡ እግዚ<supplied reason="lost"
                        >አብሔር</supplied></q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d17" type="miniature">
                        <locus target="#189r"/>
                        <desc><persName ref="PRS13687JosephArim"/> and <persName
                              ref="PRS13688Nicodemus"/> prepare the <term key="deadjesus">body of
                                 <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/></term> for burial. <q
                              xml:lang="am">ዮሴፍና፡ ኒቆዲሞስ፡ እንደገነዙት፡ እምቤታችን፡ እንዳለቀሰች፡ ክርስቶ<supplied
                                 reason="lost">ስ</supplied>፡ እንደሩቅ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዝም፡ በላችሁ፡ አትገንዙኝ፡ ቅዱስ፡
                              እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ኃይል፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሕያው፡ ዘኢይመውት፡ እያላችሁ፡ ነውጅ፡
                        እንዳል፡</q></desc></decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d18">
                        <locus target="#6r #11r #20v #24v #29vb #36r #40r #43v #48r #101rb #114r"/>
                        <desc>Elaborate, coloured (blue, red, yellow and occasionally also green and
                           violet), horizontal ornamental bands (ḥarags) over columns a–b (or over
                           column b only), with three lateral extensions reaching halfway across the
                           page, featuring interlaces and floral motifs.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d19">
                        <locus target="#109vb"/>
                        <desc>A line of blue, black and red dots for separating parts of the
                           text.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d20">
                        <locus target="#183vb"/>
                        <desc>A line of black and red dots for separating parts of the text.</desc>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
